sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant API as Steam Storefront API
    participant SCR as NB_Steam_Reviews<br/>(scraper · plain Jupyter)
    participant LZ as OneLake<br/>/Files/Steam/Reviews/
    participant AQ as loadReviews<br/>(audit view)
    participant BRZ as NB_Steam_Reviews_Bronze
    participant VC as versionControl<br/>(CDF watermark)
    participant MED as Silver → Gold<br/>(CDF-incremental)

    rect rgba(254, 205, 211, 0.94)
    Note over SCR,AQ: pl_Steam_API · hourly · no Spark cluster
    AQ-->>SCR: vw_loadReviews snapshot (top-N + cursor + watermark)
    SCR->>API: scrape (ThreadPool · tenacity retry · 403 kill-switch)
    API-->>SCR: review JSON
    SCR->>LZ: write batched JSON
    SCR->>AQ: insert execution row (is_loaded = 0)
    end

    rect rgba(221, 214, 254, 0.94)
    Note over BRZ,MED: pl_Steam_Reviews_Medallion_Incremental · daily · Spark
    AQ-->>BRZ: poll is_loaded = 0 rows
    LZ-->>BRZ: read the landed batches
    BRZ->>AQ: set is_loaded = 1 (after successful upsert)
    VC-->>MED: source delta version (watermark gate)
    Note right of MED: CDF _change_type IN (insert, update_postimage)<br/>MERGE-on-hash · SCD Type 1 · re-runs are no-ops
    MED->>VC: advance watermark
    end
